snippet.title: Tome of Heroes
snippet.description:
Real time, competitive and high skill cap player versus player on your mobile phone! Build a team of heroes around your strategy and compete versus other players around the world!

Get it on iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewSoftware?id=1227062768&mt=8
Get it on Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pulciu.tomeofheroes

Learn more:
http://www.tomeofheroes.com/
https://twitter.com/tomeofheroes
https://www.facebook.com/TomeOfHeroes
